data.description: Welcome home to 10610 Leitrim Way! This lovely three-bedroom house features one full bathroom, and the primary bedroom is equipped with an attached half bathroom for added convenience. The garage has been converted into a living room, providing extra living space within the home. The property boasts a spacious backyard, offering ample outdoor space for various activities or landscaping. Inside, the kitchen is adorned with granite countertops, adding a touch of sophistication. The house features vinyl plank flooring, which is not only aesthetically pleasing but also durable and easy to maintain. Roof is two years old. Home has water softener and reverse osmosis drinking water at kitchen sink. You don't want to miss all this gorgeous home has to offer!
